The paper proposes a technique for quantization of deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed technique is applicable to a variety of DNN architectures, which suggests a broader scope and potential relevance to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural engineering (cs.NE).
